- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with dialogue-based interfaces and natural language processing for chatbots. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as chatbots are a popular application of AI. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses how the chatbot can help users find and discover open government datasets. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper discusses the potential benefits of open data for government transparency and citizen participation. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of open government datasets.
